                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable T</hi> 21.) I went with Lake to the prisoner's house—the landlord would not let me in for about half an hour—I heard a smash of glass, and gave Lane the light—I told him to go to the spot—he came back with his umbrella—I took the prisoner into custody.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I carried away a stick, or umbrella.</p>
